<D>__{...so to these two young people, we wish them a long and happy life together and would like to play their song. the platters "only you".}
<A>__{the band starts to play "only you". people applaud. harriet and charlie just stare at each other. he knows. the older couple at the next table, mr. & mrs. levenstein, lean over to their table.}
<C>__{mr. levenstein}
