<A>__{charlie finds himself in the middle of the dance floor dancing slowly with harriet. he's scared out of his mind. the music plays in the background. harriet smiles strangely at him. he tries to smile back, checking all the exits, planning an escape. then suddenly, call it luckily, mr. levenstein, interrupts:}
<C>__{mr. levenstein}
<D>__{excuse me. could i cut in on your dance?}
