<B>__{lights are out.}
<A>__{in the dimmest of lights provided from the cloud covered moon outside, charlie runs across the dance floor, fighting for an exit to the outside. he arrives in someone's arms on his way.}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{i need your help! you have to help me! i've married a...!}
<A>__{the lights go back on and charlie is in harriet's arms again. her face is near menacing now. she smiles a very disturbed grin. he doesn't know what to say.}
